DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to compare different culture conditions. The effect of the type of incubator (standard versus mini-incubator) and the effect of the oxygen concentration (5% versus 20%) will be evaluated on the embryo quality
DOC.brief_title: Impact of Culture Conditions on the Embryo Quality
DOC.criteria: embryos of patients younger than 36 years old embryos of patients older than 36 years old
